Schell Games LLC (the “
Schell,
” “
we,
” “
us,
” or “
our
”) is committed to privacy and data protection. This Privacy Policy and Notice at Collection (“
Privacy Notice
”) applies to personal information we collect from you, through our interactions with you, through the videogame known as Among Us VR (“
AUVR
”), as well as how we use and protect personal information. You may download a copy of this Privacy Notice at
https://schellgames.com/among-us-vr-privacy-policy.
YOUR PRIVACY IS IMPORTANT TO US. PLEASE READ THIS PRIVACY NOTICE TO LEARN ABOUT THE INFORMATION THAT SCHELL COLLECT FROM YOU AND HOW SCHELL USES THAT INFORMATION. BY USING AUVR, YOU CONSENT TO THE COLLECTION, USE AND TRANSFER OF PERSONAL INFORMATION AS DESCRIBED IN THIS PRIVACY NOTICE. IF YOU HAVE NOT DONE SO ALREADY PLEASE REVIEW THE AUVR TERMS OF USE AT
https://www.innersloth.com/among-us-vr-terms-of-use/.
IF YOU DO NOT AGREE WITH ANY PART OF THIS PRIVACY NOTICE, THEN PLEASE DO NOT USE AUVR.
INNERSLOTH LLC (“
INNERSLOTH
”) OWNS AUVR AND ENGAGES SCHELL GAMES LLC TO DEVELOP, HOST, AND PROVIDE PLAYER SUPPORT FOR AUVR. THAT MEANS INNERSLOTH DOES NOT COLLECT, RECEIVE, SHARE, OR PROCESS ANY PERSONAL INFORMATION ABOUT YOU FROM AUVR. HOWEVER, IN THE EVENT THAT SCHELL’S BUSINESS RELATIONSHIP WITH INNERSLOTH ENDS, SCHELL WILL TRANSFER PERSONAL INFORMATION ABOUT YOU, THAT SCHELL RETAINS AT THE TIME OF SUCH TRANSFER, TO INNERSLOTH FOR YOUR CONTINUED, UNINTERRUPTED USE OF AUVR. IF YOU DO NOT AGREE TO SUCH TRANSFER, DO NOT USE OR PLAY AUVR.
